  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ffe91d8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGnO6FoIjc1erhKDlnMSurfnVLFqLo5vVzU3qODsRibIn9OanYOnY6HrTXSkhNgDt3FvgxGiaxiak88VA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天，MiniMax发布新一代语音生成模型Speech 2.5，再次刷新全球最强语音模型的上限。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;XQi9detN2oeH21x0CDXcws2Ln2d&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;今天，MiniMax 发布新一代语音生成模型 Speech 2.5，再次刷新全球强语音模型的上限。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1d&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7212432851684294659&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;bb40761f-c9b6-408c-945b-7590f0f906d3&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:6,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:49},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;KvqAddCHgodTCyx7bDNce47dnYf&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相比5月发布的</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5MTA3NzcxMQ==&amp;mid=2247486527&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2b28d0db71c0db144af9e29d70e738d6&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Speech 02\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Speech 02</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，Speech 2.5有三大新突破：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">多语种表现力更强、音色复刻更像、40个语种覆盖更广。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"font-size:36px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 5px 0px 2px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 2px solid rgb(240, 60, 22);padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"width:100%;line-height:1;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">多语种表现力飞跃：</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">中文全球最强，英文等多语种全面提升</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;XQi9detN2oeH21x0CDXcws2Ln2d&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;多语种表现力飞跃：不仅中文全球最强，英文等多语种也全面提升&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+t&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7212432851684294659&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;bold&quot;,&quot;true&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ordered&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;1f3ac441-e835-4ff3-9b1e-73c3ca04ab8d&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:14,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:29},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;L4Sld54tNopE4vxz58qcirlVnDe&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">字错率、相似度、自然韵律度超越前代Speech 02，英文相似度显著提升，40种语言随心切换，商务会议、日常对话、英文播客再无“机械感”困扰。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;XQi9detN2oeH21x0CDXcws2Ln2d&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;字错率、相似度、自然韵律度超越前代Speech02，英文相似度显著提升，40种语言随心切换，商务会议、日常对话、英文播客再无“机械感”困扰。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1y&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7212432851684294659&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;1c08a59c-3a3c-4f9d-b681-4dc6e7a1d021&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:16,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:70},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;HLBgd2vzfoma6FxS3ZQcvdxYnXf&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">例如，立下复仇誓言的哈姆雷特，和</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">充满激情的西班牙体育赛事解说员</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;XQi9detN2oeH21x0CDXcws2Ln2d&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;立下复仇誓言的哈姆雷特：&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+c&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7212432851684294659&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;6fdd26ce-82dc-4508-9910-2df6485327fa&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:18,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:12},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;AwaFde03wot6XWx1HxJc24D6n1f&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -20px 0px 0px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 23px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Remember? Yea, from the tables of my memory, I'll wipe away all trivial fond records. All saws of books, all forms, all pressures past, that youth and observation copied there. And then commandment all alone shall live within the book and volume of my brain, unmixed with baser matter. Yes, yes by heaven.</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;line-height: 1.5em;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -20px 0px 0px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 23px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">¡Arranca el genio por la derecha, deja atrás a uno, se saca de encima al segundo, entra al área, prepara el remate...¡GOLAZO MONUMENTAL! ¡Una obra de arte que sella la victoria y desata la locura total!</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"font-size:36px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 5px 0px 2px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 2px solid rgb(240, 60, 22);padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"width:100%;line-height:1;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">音色复刻更“像”：</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">跨语种口音、风格、情绪，细节神还原</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;XQi9detN2oeH21x0CDXcws2Ln2d&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;音色复刻更“像”：跨语种口音、风格、情绪，细节神还原&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+q&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7212432851684294659&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;bold&quot;,&quot;true&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ordered&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;e346f3be-abab-467c-851d-3fa926e87757&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:31,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:26},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;M2SXdaQ1FoBDraxJ7W3c4MQSnOb&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">行业天花板级精度：跨语种复刻口音保留、同语种不同地区的口音保留、特殊年龄的声音复刻等</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">极限场景下，依然“声”动逼真</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用英国女王的经典发音来介绍最新的 Speech 2.5会是什么样？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -20px 0px 0px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 23px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hello everyone. We're thrilled to introduce the next generation of our voice model: MiniMax Speech 2.5. Building on its predecessor, Speech 2.0, this new version is more powerful than ever. But where it truly shines is in its incredible realism. The model masterfully captures the subtle nuances of the human voice——from trailing intonation and vocal style, to the full spectrum of emotion, all reproduced with stunning authenticity.</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从停顿、节奏、到发音处理，模型保持了纯正的“女王腔”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">跨语种复刻也不再话下，同一音色在意大利语、英语间的切换，依旧保留口音特色细节：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -20px 0px 0px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 23px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Questa è la mia vera voce. I find speaking English a bit difficult. It's like trying to speak Italian without using hand gestures.</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"font-size:36px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 5px 0px 2px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 2px solid rgb(240, 60, 22);padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"width:100%;font-size:15px;line-height:1;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">多语种增至40个：</span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">多样化高质量音色库，全球化畅行无阻</span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;XQi9detN2oeH21x0CDXcws2Ln2d&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;多语种增至40个：更多样化高质量音色库，全球化畅行无阻&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+r&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7212432851684294659&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;bold&quot;,&quot;true&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ordered&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;d08ef23a-3d0a-4e8d-b9a2-80da19e77271&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:49,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&q