079\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=98a3d858&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGnO6FoIjc1erhKDlnMSurfn0wQbE6Gsd5WlmlynRWIOXMQPvqQpHicqDfyiaNEoffn0HsWDvg1ArhnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">谁需要 Speech 2.5？应用场景一键解锁：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">企业客户：多语种客服、跨国广告配音成本骤降，省下百万配音费，10分钟生成全球40国产品宣传片配音</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">创作者：逼真的个人声线细节复刻，一人开口说40国语言，全球短视频爆款轻松造，创作者表达无国界</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">教育者：小众语言课件制作周期从2周 → 10分钟，定制跨国方言教材，全球知识更“接地气”</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Speech&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2.5，在Speech&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">02全球语音模型榜单第一的基础上再升级，并同时延续了全球最高的性价比</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前，MiniMax Speech语音模型已在全球被广泛采用</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。在海外，Vapi，Pipecat等Agent平台选择使用MiniMax Speech提供服务，Hedra、Icon、Syllaby等头部AI应用也已接入MiniMax Speech。国内，高途教育、喜马拉雅、网易、Rokid眼镜等头部平台及产品都选择了MiniMax Speech。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100003133\" data-ratio=\"0.604309500489716\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2042\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3fb836e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGnO6FoIjc1erhKDlnMSurfnfvJiavmhQ49FLXt0ia0aSHuBLkrduppTSbmWQhDAUibuVbxquW1Sl2plA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Speech 2.5已全球上线，欢迎登录MiniMax开放平台或MiniMax Audio官网</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">体验。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">MiniMax开放平台：</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color:rgb(36,91,219);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 [